todoyu assets extension changelog

assets 1.1.0 (requires core >= 2.1) - not released yet
	* Feature: Added task asset upload to task creation form
	* Feature: Cleanup of Rights Management
	* Feature: Cleanup (topical order and readability) of extension config (init.php) file
	* Feature: Forms restyled
	* Updated loading structure: (core: boot.php, init: request,) extensions: init.php
	* Feature: Changed locale format


assets 1.0.6 - not released yet
	* Feature: Added changelog


